translations: 通用目标文件格式（Common Object File Format）

sentences.sentence: COFF format does not support the GROUP directive and zero-length sections.
sentences.translation: coff格式不支援GROUP指示词与长度为零的区段。

sentences.sentence: When LINK automatically converts this type of OMF objects to COFF, this error may occur.
sentences.translation: 当LINK自动将这种型别的OM f目的档转换成COFF时，便可能会发生这种错误。

sentences.sentence: Loads the assembly with a common object file format (COFF) -based image containing an emitted assembly.
sentences.translation: 加载带有基于通用对象文件格式(COFF)的映像的程序集，该映像包含已发出的程序集。
